snippet.title: Bubble Therapy | Gamma Music - Increase Focus, Creativity
snippet.description:
Bubble Therapy | Gamma Music - Increase Focus, Creativity
#gammamusic #gammahealing #40hzmusic

1 hour calming healing music using visual bubble therapy as well as bubble musical motifs representation centred around a 40HZ binaural beat. The composition is written in tune with the gamma waves within our brain to really focus in on that region of the brain to help with increasing focus, creativity and learning. Use during study, relaxation, sleep or relaxation.

What is Bubble Therapy ?
Bubble therapy is a simple activity that involves bubbles and can be used for a variety of purposes, including:

* Stress relief: Blowing bubbles can help lower blood pressure and heart rate, and can be a meditative technique that can help relieve stress.¬†

* Mindfulness: Bubbles can help you focus on a single activity and cultivate mindfulness.¬†

* Calming: Blowing bubbles can have a calming effect on the nervous system.¬†

* Sensory processing: The physical act of blowing bubbles can help people organize, focus, and calm their bodies.¬†

* Speech and motor development: Bubbles can help with speech and motor development.¬†

* Teaching calming breathing: Blowing bubbles can help  people learn to breathe in a slow, calm way, which can reduce stress, anxiety, and panic.¬†

* Creating a shared activity: Bubbles can be a fun activity for both children and adults.

What is Gamma Healing?
Gamma healing is a technique that uses gamma brain waves to create a peak state of consciousness. Gamma brain waves are the fastest brain waves produced by the brain, and are associated with higher brain functions like memory, cognition, and problem-solving as well as creativity, new ideas and thinking outside the box. Gamma healing can help eliminate limiting beliefs, anxiety, fear, and doubt. 

benefits of gamma brain waves:
*Improved memory: Gamma waves can help improve working memory.

*Increased concentration: Gamma waves can help you achieve higher concentration levels.

*Improved cognitive function: Gamma waves can help improve your cognitive function and problem-solving ability.

*Increased awareness: Gamma waves can help increase your awareness and mindfulness.

*Increased brain function: Gamma waves can promote higher states of awareness and increased brain function during meditation.

snippet.title: 8D Music | Thunder Therapy
snippet.description:
8D Music | Thunder Therapy 
#thundertherapy #8DMusic #EMDRTherapymusic

3 Hour bilateral stimulation music incorporating thunder therapy, 8d audio, EMDR therapy music techniques and anti anxiety sounds.

Our brain craves sensory input, and the sound of thunder can appease the brain‚Äôs demands, which calms us down. The low frequency rumble of thunder can activate our parasympathetic nervous system, which is responsible for promoting feelings of rest and relaxation. Thunder has a deep rooted connection with us to nature, thunderstorms mimic the natural rhythm of our environment evoking a sense of familiarity and safety. This connection combined with 8D sounds creates a perfect recipe for stress release, anti anxiety and removing stored up negative negative energy. Thunder sounds also have the power to reduce stress hormone levels, lower blood pressure and promote a sense of peace and tranquility. Giving us the ability to unwind, find balance and harmony.

WHAT IS BILATERAL STIMULATION MUSIC?
Bilateral music helps the brain process the stress or traumatic memories so that the person can eventually think about the stressful memories without triggering severe anxiety or stress. Bilateral music is calming, soothing and relaxing to the mind body and soul. Bilateral music is music that gently shifts from one ear to ear, and directs eye movement and awareness towards different parts of the brain as we orient towards the sounds.

Reduction in anxiety, PTSD, and other stress-related disorders: By helping the body transition from fight-or-flight to rest-and-digest mode, bilateral stimulation can ease feelings of anxiety, PTSD, and other stress-related disorders‚Äîincluding social anxiety disorder‚Äîand promote a sense of overall relaxation.

snippet.title: Dopamine Detox | Overcome Addiction
snippet.description:
Dopamine Detox | Overcome Addiction
#overcomeaddiction #dopaminedetox #healingfrequencies

A healing frequency session to help curb addiction. Addiction can come in many forms: substances, food, OCD, emotion, mental, computers, phone / social media addiction, even depression can become an addiction.

Addiction is when you have a strong physical, mental or psychological urge to do something or use something. It is a dependence on a substance or activity even if you know that it causes you harm. It can impact your daily life and spiritual progression.

Addictive behaviour source comes from the frontal cortex within the brain. When the receptors get disrupted it decreases the ability to choose not to partake in the addiction. It impairs the self control mechanism in the brain and the doorway to a dopamine hit is opened even more, needing more and more of the stimulus to get a desired effect. 

The key to overcome addiction is to do a dopamine fasting cleanse regularly throughout the rest of life. This means to balance the whole system by not partaking in anything that will make you overtly happy or overtly sad. Initially the timeframe for this will be 90-100 percent of the time until the dopamine receptors have calmed down. Then this can be lessened slowly to a more sustainable achievement for the rest of your life. This varies in all people - be aware of how much stimuli you can take and adjust the fasting stage accordingly.

We have centred this frequency session around -Impulse control, Emotional control to help dampen that urge and lessen the dopamine hit you crave.
